* text=auto eol=lf

# D-13 (#483): pin the self-hosted font binaries as binary. `text=auto` above
# would otherwise leave it to git's NUL-byte heuristic, and this repo also runs
# core.autocrlf=true — a woff2 that ever got line-ending-converted would be
# silently corrupted (the face fails to decode, and the app falls back with no
# build error). Explicit beats heuristic for a file whose corruption is invisible
# until render.
*.woff2 binary
